<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>404 — Página no encontrada</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/favicon.png">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Outfit:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --color-primary: #2E4F40;
            --color-secondary: #1a2b22;
            --color-text: #F5F2EC;
            --color-text-dim: rgba(245, 242, 236, 0.6);
            --color-accent: #4ade80;
            --card-bg: rgba(26, 43, 34, 0.8);
            --border-color: rgba(214, 232, 227, 0.1);
        }

        *,
        *::before,
        *::after {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--color-primary), var(--color-secondary));
            color: var(--color-text);
            font-family: 'Outfit', 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 40px 20px;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 560px;
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .card {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 50px 40px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .error-label {
            display: inline-block;
            font-size: 0.72rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: 0.2em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: var(--color-accent);
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        .error-code {
            font-size: clamp(5rem, 18vw, 9rem);
            font-weight: 700;
            line-height: 1;
            color: var(--color-text);
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .error-code span {
            color: var(--color-accent);
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: var(--color-text);
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            color: var(--color-text-dim);
            line-height: 1.7;
            margin-bottom: 36px;
        }

        .actions {
            display: flex;
            gap: 12px;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            padding: 10px 24px;
            background: var(--color-accent);
            color: var(--color-secondary);
            border: none;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-decoration: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: opacity 0.2s;
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            opacity: 0.85;
        }

        .btn-secondary {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            padding: 10px 24px;
            background: rgba(46, 79, 64, 0.5);
            color: var(--color-text);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            text-decoration: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background 0.2s;
        }

        .btn-secondary:hover {
            background: var(--color-primary);
        }

        .divider {
            width: 4px;
            height: 40px;
            background: var(--color-accent);
            border-radius: 2px;
            margin: 0 auto 28px;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 28px;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: var(--color-text-dim);
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="divider"></div>
            <div class="error-label">Error de navegación</div>

            <div class="error-code">4<span>0</span>4</div>

            <h1>Página no encontrada</h1>
            <p>La ruta que buscas no existe o fue movida.<br>Revisa la URL o regresa al inicio.</p>

            <div class="actions">
                <a href="/home" class="btn-primary">
                    <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"
                        stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <path d="M3 12L12 3l9 9" />
                        <path d="M9 21V12h6v9" />
                    </svg>
                    Ir al Inicio
                </a>
                <a href="javascript:history.back()" class="btn-secondary">
                    <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"
                        stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                        <path d="M19 12H5" />
                        <path d="M12 19l-7-7 7-7" />
                    </svg>
                    Volver atrás
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">Zona Protegida — JWT Demo</div>
    </div>

</body>

</html>